if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('sys_purview')
and type = 'U')
drop table sys_purview
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: sys_purview */
/*==============================================================*/
create table sys_purview (
PurviewCode nvarchar(100) not null,
Name nvarchar(100) null default '',
Url nvarchar(500) null,
ParentCode nvarchar(100) null,
Sort float not null,
AppTime datetime not null default getdate(),
Isdel bit not null default 0,
constraint PK_SYS_PURVIEW primary key (PurviewCode)
)
go
